        %section
          %h2 Content storage problem

          %p What is the motivation of the network to store your content?
          %p Ethereum has its own content storage motivation
          %p Can this model be applied to content?

          %ul
            %li.fragment There is a way to motivate the network to store your content
            %li.fragment There is a way to ask service provider for content storage confirmation
            %li.fragment There is NO WAY to ensure service provider makes your content available
        %section
          %h2 Dynamic Content

          %p 
            Every time you hear about some success in decentralized content storage and deliver
            no one is even telling you its only for static content
          %p There is no technology to store dynamic content in a decentralized way in development


